id: monica-release-pat-secret
title: Configure RELEASE_PAT for protected-master auto-release pushes
description: The release environment contains NPM_TOKEN but lacks the maintainer token required to push a checked release commit and tag through protected master and trigger the downstream tag workflow.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[4]: blocked,github-actions,release,secrets
created_at: "2026-07-21T17:44:21.372Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-21T17:54:00.660Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-21T17:53:59.698Z"
author: codex-auto-release
estimated_minutes: 15
acceptance_criteria: The release environment lists RELEASE_PAT and a push-enabled Auto Release completes the protected-master handoff.
parent: monica-auto-release
reviewer: codex-auto-release
risk: high
confidence: high
sprint: release-activation
release: next
reporter: codex-auto-release
severity: high
environment: GitHub environment release for unbraind/monica-cli
repro_steps: Run gh secret list --env release and observe only NPM_TOKEN; production Auto Release with push=true fails its explicit preflight.
resolution: Configured and validated the required release environment credentials without storing their values in repository or pm data.
expected_result: The release environment lists NPM_TOKEN and RELEASE_PAT and npm authentication resolves to the package owner.
actual_result: Both required secret names are configured and npm authentication succeeds as the expected package owner.
customer_impact: Scheduled releases remain safely disabled until a maintainer provisions the secret.
comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T17:44:21.372Z",codex-auto-release,"pm-cli release environment confirms the matching secret name exists there,but GitHub does not expose secret values for copying."
  "2026-07-21T17:53:57.993Z",codex-auto-release,Validated the npm credential with npm whoami and configured both required secret names in the protected GitHub release environment. No credential values were read into or stored in pm data.
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T17:44:21.372Z",codex-auto-release,Provision this secret directly in GitHub; never store its value in tracked pm metadata.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T17:44:21.372Z",codex-auto-release,GITHUB_TOKEN-generated pushes do not provide the downstream workflow trigger semantics used by the reference pipeline.
files[1]{path,scope,note}:
  .github/workflows/auto-release.yml,project,Fails fast when RELEASE_PAT is absent
tests[1]{command,scope,timeout_seconds}:
  gh secret list --env release,project,60
docs[1]{path,scope,note}:
  docs/RELEASE-MANAGEMENT.md,project,Secret requirements and recovery procedure
close_reason: Required release environment credentials are configured and authentication is validated.
body: "Add RELEASE_PAT directly in GitHub environment release. The token must have repository contents write permission and protected-branch bypass capability. Do not place the token in pm, source files, logs, or chat. After configuration, dispatch Auto Release with dry_run=true and push=false, then perform the first intentional push-enabled run."
